Sentencas: Single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell (SC-SOFC) microstacks with V-Shaped congener-electrode-facing configuration were fabricated and operated successfully in a box-like stainless steel chamber.
Titulo: Study of a Single-Chamber Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Microstack with V-Shaped Congener-Electrode-Facing Configuration

Sentencas: Two gas channels with small gas inlets were used to transport the fuel and oxygen to the anodes and cathodes, respectively.
Titulo: Study of a Single-Chamber Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Microstack with V-Shaped Congener-Electrode-Facing Configuration

Sentencas: The temperature of an anode-facing-anode two-cell stack was higher than that of a cathode-facing-cathode two-cell stack during the test procedure.
Titulo: Study of a Single-Chamber Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Microstack with V-Shaped Congener-Electrode-Facing Configuration

Sentencas: For a three-cell stack, the cell in the middle region presented the highest power output.
Titulo: Study of a Single-Chamber Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Microstack with V-Shaped Congener-Electrode-Facing Configuration

Sentencas: The open circuit voltage (OCV) and maximum power output of the three-cell stack in a gas mixture of 100?sccm N2, 120?sccm CH4, and 80?sccm O2 were 3.0?V and 413?mW, respectively.
Titulo: Study of a Single-Chamber Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Microstack with V-Shaped Congener-Electrode-Facing Configuration
